<h3>Recommended changes</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Corn starts with $1 less</li>
    <li>Factory costs $8</li>
    <li>University costs $7</li>
    <li>Do not use Office + Trading Post</li>
    <li>Do not use Forest House + Hacienda (player suggestion)</li>
    <li>Do not use Villa + Jeweler (player suggestion)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Clarifications</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Craftsman: takes bonus good last; must produce goods to receive privilege</li>
    <li>Settler: taking a tile is optional</li>
    <li>Mayor: privilege is optional; may store excess colonists on windrose, but <u>only</u> if there are no available circles</li>
    <li>Buccaneer
        <ul>
            <li>Do not add doubloons at end of round</li>
            <li>May not take again until another player takes it - use the reward tile</li>
            <li>Raid: Colonists must be added to buildings/tiles - cannot go to windrose</li>
            <li>Kidnap:
                <ul>
                    <li>Take any doubloons on the selected role</li>
                    <li>No one else takes kidnapped role: +$3</li>
                    <li>Else: play the kidnapped role as normal</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>

